###Interesting expressions 001


This means that vowels tend to either be the same or similar, making words easier to pronounce than they may look.

come across

Check if there are any pending changes to be saved.
They just happen to look the same.
seems to be pretty cool.
We went with another family of our friends.
Cakes consist of five components. (consist of).

Well, you better have a word with him then!

To be fair, Turkish is a very regular language. Once you learn the basic rules, it should get easier. The course has been released only a few days ago, give it a bit more time. :)
